Apollo’s Black Says U.S. Economy May Remain in ‘Holding Pattern’

-- B y   L y u b o v   P r o n i n a
-- 
2011-09-16T10:46:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/apollo-s-black-says-u-s-economy-may-remain-in-holding-pattern-.html
Leon Black , head of private equity
giant Apollo Global Management LLC, said the U.S. economy is set
to remain in a “holding pattern.” He spoke at a conference in
 Russia ’s Black Sea resort of Sochi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
